\begin_layout Section
Clock Drawer
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Calls 
\family typewriter
Time()
\family default
 and goes into an infinite loop that:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Prints time.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Increment time by 10 clicks (1 ms).
\end_layout

