Controller
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Not implemented in tc1.
 The train controller manages: 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
A train's position
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Expected sensor that would be triggered for a train engineer, and does path
